OL,3,CMan convicted of murdering 25-year-old
OL,4,Cwith knife
OL,6,FA man has been found guilty of
OL,7,Fmurdering a 25-year-old man with a
OL,8,Fknife in Bristol.
OL,10,FShakawan Siddiqi, 32, attacked Kunta
OL,11,FCeesay with a knife in Stapleton Road
OL,12,Fduring an altercation in the street.
OL,13,FThe fatal incident happened on Friday
OL,14,F20 September last year, with Mr Ceesay
OL,15,Fdying from his injuries.
OL,17,FSiddiqi, of St Pauls, was found guilty
OL,18,Fby a jury after a two-and-a-half week
OL,19,Ftrial at Bristol Crown Court.
