OL,6,FMr Ceesay's family said he was 'kind,
OL,7,Fbubbly and loving' and that their
OL,8,Flives will never be the same again.
OL,10,FThe jury was told it is still unclear
OL,11,Fwhether Mr Ceesay knew Siddiqi, but
OL,12,Fthere may have been a previous dispute
OL,13,Fover a small amount of money.
OL,15,FThe court was told Mr Ceesay picked up
OL,16,FSiddiqi's bike which had been left
OL,17,Foutside a Post Office. A short time
OL,18,Flater an altercation happened between
OL,19,Fthe pair and within about 30 seconds,
OL,20,FCeesay had been fatally wounded.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/8
