OL,6,FSiddiqi left the scene before police
OL,7,Fand ambulance arrived. The jury heard
OL,8,Fhe disposed of the knife and changed
OL,9,Fhis clothing, and that he was arrested
OL,10,Fthe next day.
OL,12,FAhead of the trial Siddiqi accepted he
OL,13,Fstabbed Mr Ceesay but claimed he had
OL,14,Fbeen acting in self-defence. He also
OL,15,Fdenied one count of possession of a
OL,16,Fbladed article in a public place.
OL,18,FThe jury however found the 32-year-old
OL,19,Fguilty of both offences and he will be
OL,20,Fsentenced at a later date.
