OL,6,FMr Ceesay's family have welcomed the
OL,7,Fverdict and paid tribute to him in a
OL,8,Fstatement, saying he would "always
OL,9,Fhelped his family and friends whenever
OL,10,Fhe could".
OL,12,F"Everybody liked him and they would
OL,13,Fconfide in him because of how open he
OL,14,Fwas.
OL,16,F"It is so sad for the family that
OL,17,FKunta was taken from us far too soon
OL,18,Fand he has been robbed of the chance
OL,19,Fto grow old, create his own family and
OL,20,Freach his dreams.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/8
