OL,3,CMan convicted of murdering 25-year-old
OL,4,Cwith knife
OL,6,F"It's difficult to comprehend the
OL,7,Fsenseless way that Kunta has lost his
OL,8,Flife and how difficult it will be for
OL,9,Fall of us to have to live without him.
OL,11,F"Whilst our hearts and lives will
OL,12,Fnever be the same, we the family of
OL,13,FKunta trusted the justice system and
OL,14,Fthe jurors to make the right decision
OL,15,Fin this case. We are so grateful for
OL,16,Fthe work done by the police and
OL,17,Fprosecution in bringing Siddiqi to
OL,18,Fjustice.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/8
