OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F434A1744232007
OL,3,CMan convicted of murdering 25-year-old
OL,4,Cwith knife
OL,6,F"We are happy with the verdict and
OL,7,Falthough it won't bring Kunta back, it
OL,8,Fhas reinforced our faith in the
OL,9,Fjustice system and the police.
OL,11,F"Kunta's life meant something, and we
OL,12,Fhope that this will serve as a
OL,13,Freminder for people to be cautious,
OL,14,Flead with kindness and love in their
OL,15,Flives."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/8
