OL,6,FDetective Inspector Deb Hatch, of the
OL,7,FMajor Crime Investigation Team, said:
OL,8,F"The moving words from Kunta's family
OL,9,Fshow how dearly loved he was and how
OL,10,Fdeeply they continue to grieve his
OL,11,Fdeath.
OL,13,F"Their support of the police
OL,14,Finvestigation over the past seven
OL,15,Fmonths has been overwhelming and is
OL,16,Fhugely appreciated. A specially
OL,17,Ftrained officer has provided them with
OL,18,Fsupport throughout and we are pleased
OL,19,Fto have secured a guilty verdict for
OL,20,Fthem and answers around what happened
OL,21,Fon that fateful day last September."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/8
