OL,6,FDI Hatch continued: "The claim from
OL,7,FSiddiqi he was carrying a knife for
OL,8,Fprotection and self-defence was not
OL,9,Faccepted by the jury.
OL,11,F"Carrying a knife in fact increases
OL,12,Fthe level of danger, both for that
OL,13,Findividual or anyone who they
OL,14,Fencounter.
OL,16,F"Siddiqi made the decision to carry a
OL,17,Fknife with him that day and it was a
OL,18,Fdecision that ultimately cost Kunta
OL,19,Fhis life."
